    "ELNet MC-8 is an 8/24 channel counter",
    "Three-phase energy measurements in Touz\nDisplay of all electricity measurements\nSupport for 8 three-phase or 24 single-phase channels.\nmeasurement accuracy 0.2%\n1600 samples per cycle.\nView all electricity measurements.\nCollection of daily energy data for 4 months.\nInternal memory for collecting data in different sections.\nAngia measurements according to the Israeli Ta'oz.\nMeasuring harmonics up to the 64th harmonic\nSupport for multiple languages including Hebrew.\nRS485 communication\nTCP/IP communication is built into the device\nSupport for BACnet, Modbus protocols\nHigh quality 240X320 color graphic screen.\nGraphical waveform display.\nInstallation on a simple and easy panel rail on the front of the board.\nEmail support",
